Package filebrowser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NavigationParent
    An interface to make connection between the file explorer and its parent frame.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileExplorer
    A panel which contains a navigator to browse files
    FileNavigator
    A JTree component which can navigate through files on the disk.
    FileNode
    A class to represent a single file node on the file navigator
    PathedFile
    This class present files for file node with contains references itself, parent and grandparents
    RealTimeFolderWatcher
    A class to listen the file changes in a directory
    TreeDirectoryPopupMenu
    The PopupMenu class for folders in the file explorer.
    TreeFilePopupMenu
    The PopupMenu class for files in the file explorer.
    TreeJavaFilePopupMenu
    The PopupMenu class for java source files in the file explorer.
    TreeProjectPopupMenu
    This class represent a pop up menu for project root
